  "slug": "enchanted-books-from-mars",
  "title": "Mars's Enchanted Book Textures",
  "description": "Changes the textures of enchanted books for better clarity",
  "body": "<h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XLhWGhC.png\" alt=\"Title\"/></h1>\n<center><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> \n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/2CUh6gMuCt\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1027252425960198165?color=5b6ee1&amp;label=Discord&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://patreon.com/MarsThePlanet\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint.svg?url=https%3A%2F%2Fshieldsio-patreon.vercel.app%2Fapi%3Fusername%3DMarsThePlanet%26type%3Dpatrons&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/enchanted-books-from-mars\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/1268200?color=F16436&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=Curseforge&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"CurseForge\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/enchanted-books-from-mars\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/enchanted-books-from-mars?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=modrinth&amp;color=00AF5C\" alt=\"Modrinth\" /></a>\n</strong></h5></center>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This mod gives every enchanted book its own unique texture, making it much easier to find the one you need at a glance. It is based on a <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/different-textures-for-enchanted-books\">resource pack</a> I previously made, which requires an additional mod implementing CITs to work. With this mod, you do not need to download a resource pack and depend on separate CIT mods that may vary between Minecraft versions and mod loaders.</p></center>\n<center>\n<br />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Examples of the new textures</h2>\n<p>New Textures <b>ON</b><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ClzoG9Q.png\" width=\"460\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gF6wPij.png\" width=\"460\" /></p>\n<p>New Textures <b>OFF</b><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/buQW2Sc.png\" width=\"460\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Qg9kIju.png\" width=\"460\" /></p>\n</center>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Configuration</strong></summary>\n<p>You can configure this mod directly in-game or by editing the JSON file <code>config/ebooks.json</code> in your profile folder. If you're using Fabric and want to adjust the config values in-game, you'll need to install <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/modmenu\">Mod Menu</a>.</p>\n<center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>turned_on</b> - Turns the enchanted book textures from this mod on and off</p>\n</center>\n</details>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JNZ2GMV.png\"/>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/deimos-fabric-forge-neoforge\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/83sD0W8.png\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/deimos\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j2GIPnt.png\"/></a>\n</p></center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/marstheplanet\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rJIRiP5.png\" /></a></p>",
